":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"BBQ"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Air Conditioning"}],"toys":[{"label":"Zar 85 SL tender with Honda V8 (350 HP)"},{"label":"Flite Seascooter"},{"label":"Seabob F9 (with fast F9 charger)"},{"label":"Hobie Eclipse iTrek DLX (pedal kayak)"},{"label":"Nautibuoy 800 Sport (4 m x 2 m)"},{"label":"Jobe 4P Binar with rope"},{"label":"SUP (Jobe Aero Nera 10.6)"},{"label":"Snorkeling equipment"}],"entertainment":["Smart TV","Wi-Fi","Salon Stereo","Sat Tv","Salon TV"],"tenders":["Zar 85 SL tender with Honda V8 (350 HP)"]},"crew":[{"name":"Mateo Gašperov","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::a167f3a0-7f6a-11ef-b3e5-8795280763d4::assets::6c9d0100-16f6-11f0-b3f1-0154de9666d9/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":""},{"name":"IVANA VUKUSIC","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::a167f3a0-7f6a-11ef-b3e5-8795280763d4::assets::9c217690-16f6-11f0-b063-17e83781b4ff/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nikolija Baretić is a highly creative and detail-oriented Yacht Chef and Hostess with a background in fine arts and fashion design, combined with a deep passion for gastronomy. With extensive experience on board high-end sailing and motor yachts, she excels in delivering unforgettable guest experiences, from menu creation and gourmet meal preparation to elegant table settings and luxury-level service.\n\nFluent in Croatian and English, Nikolija brings excellent communication skills, flexibility, and a strong sense of hospitality. Her artistic eye and culinary talent allow her to craft personalized and visually stunning holiday experiences for discerning charter guests across the Mediterranean.\n\nAs a trained painter, she also offers a unique \"Wine & Paint\" evening onboard, inviting guests to relax and explore their creativity while enjoying curated local wines and a magical sunset setting—a thoughtful touch that blends culture and connection into every charter."},{"name":"LUKAS BO